      "closestHeading": "Tables",
      "pageNumber": 3
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "Cedar University 24 20 +4",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Tables",
      "pageNumber": 3
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "Elm College 43 53 -10",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Tables",
      "pageNumber": 3
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "Total 998 908 90",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Tables",
      "pageNumber": 3
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "Source: Fictitious data, for illustration purposes only",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Tables",
      "pageNumber": 3
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, we have something a little more complex, a nested table, i.e. a table inside",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Tables",
      "pageNumber": 3
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "another table. Additionally, the inner table has some of its cells merged. The table is",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Tables",
      "pageNumber": 3
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "displayed horizontally centered.",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Tables",
      "pageNumber": 3
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "One Two To the left is a table inside a",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Tables",
      "pageNumber": 4
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "table, with some cells",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Tables",
      "pageNumber": 4
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "Three Four merged.",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Tables",
      "pageNumber": 4
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "We end with a fancy calendar, note how much of the original formatting is",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Tables",
      "pageNumber": 4
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "preserved. Note that this table will only display correctly on relatively wide screens. In",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Tables",
      "pageNumber": 4
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "general, very wide tables or tables whose cells have fixed width requirements don’t",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Tables",
      "pageNumber": 4
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "fare well in ebooks.",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Tables",
      "pageNumber": 4
    }
  },
