      "closestHeading": "D should use.",
      "pageNumber": 5
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "1 In paged media, footnotes are usually displayed at the bottom of the text. However, in ebooks, a",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "D should use.",
      "pageNumber": 5
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "better paradigm is to make them clickable endnotes that the user can browse at her pleasure. This",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "D should use.",
      "pageNumber": 5
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "conversion is handled automatically by calibre.",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "D should use.",
      "pageNumber": 5
    }
  },
  {
