  {
    "text": "Images",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Images",
      "pageNumber": 7
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "Centered images like this are useful for large pictures that should be a focus of",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Images",
      "pageNumber": 7
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "attention.",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Images",
      "pageNumber": 7
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "There is no analogous technology in ebooks, so the conversion will usually end up",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Images",
      "pageNumber": 7
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "placing the image either centered or floating close to the point in the text where it",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Images",
      "pageNumber": 7
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "was inserted , not necessarily where it appears on the page in Word.",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Images",
      "pageNumber": 7
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "Lists",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Lists",
      "pageNumber": 8
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "All types of lists are supported by the conversion, with the exception of lists that",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Lists",
      "pageNumber": 8
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "use fancy bullets, these get converted to regular bullets.",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Lists",
      "pageNumber": 8
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "Bulleted List",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Lists",
      "pageNumber": 8
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "• One",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Lists",
      "pageNumber": 8
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "• Two",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Lists",
      "pageNumber": 8
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "Numbered List",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Lists",
      "pageNumber": 8
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "1. One, with a very long line to demonstrate that the hanging indent for the",
    "metadata": {
