  {
    "text": "ii. Two",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Lists",
      "pageNumber": 8
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "An interruption in our regularly scheduled listing, for this essential and very",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Lists",
      "pageNumber": 8
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "relevant public service announcement.",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Lists",
      "pageNumber": 8
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "iii. We now resume our normal programming",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Lists",
      "pageNumber": 8
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "iv. Four",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Lists",
      "pageNumber": 8
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "i Endnotes are typically used for longer notes, they remain endnotes when converted into ebook",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Lists",
      "pageNumber": 8
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "form, except that they have an additional backlink to make it easy to return to the current position",
    "metadata": {
      "sourceType": "pdf",
      "closestHeading": "Lists",
      "pageNumber": 8
    }
  },
  {
    "text": "after reading the note.",
